Liouville's Law

..math::
   \begin{eqnarray}
   \frac{\mathrm d \rho}{\mathrm d t}\equiv \frac{\partial \rho}{\partial t} + \sum_i \left[ \frac{\partial \rho}{\partial q_i}\dot q_i + \frac{\partial \rho}{\partial p_i}\dot p_i \right] = 0
   \end{eqnarray}






























